        "content": "<p>I'm not sure what is the obstacle here. Dan, do you want the following?</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">lemma</span> <span class=\"n\">dan_limit</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">u</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚Ñï</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚Üí</span> <span class=\"n\">‚Ñù</span><span class=\"o\">}</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">L</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">‚Ñù</span><span class=\"o\">}</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">f</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">‚Ñù</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚Üí</span> <span class=\"n\">‚Ñù</span><span class=\"o\">}</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">hu</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">tendsto</span> <span class=\"n\">u</span> <span class=\"n\">at_top</span> <span class=\"err\">$</span> <span class=\"err\">ùìù</span> <span class=\"n\">L</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n<span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">hf</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">continuous_at</span> <span class=\"n\">f</span> <span class=\"n\">L</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">huf</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚àÄ</span> <span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">u</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">f</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">u</span> <span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"o\">))</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">f</span> <span class=\"n\">L</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">L</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"k\">begin</span>\n  <span class=\"k\">have</span> <span class=\"n\">lim</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">tendsto</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">u</span> <span class=\"err\">‚àò</span> <span class=\"n\">nat</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">succ</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"n\">at_top</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"err\">ùìù</span> <span class=\"n\">L</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n    <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">tendsto_add_at_top_iff_nat</span> <span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">mpr</span> <span class=\"n\">hu</span><span class=\"o\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">rw</span> <span class=\"k\">show</span> <span class=\"n\">u</span> <span class=\"err\">‚àò</span> <span class=\"n\">nat</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">succ</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">f</span> <span class=\"err\">‚àò</span> <span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"k\">from</span> <span class=\"n\">funext</span> <span class=\"n\">huf</span> <span class=\"n\">at</span> <span class=\"n\">lim</span><span class=\"o\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">exact</span> <span class=\"n\">tendsto_nhds_unique</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">tendsto</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">comp</span> <span class=\"n\">hf</span> <span class=\"n\">hu</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"n\">lim</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">end</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
